          <node refid="T7" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1314</offset>
        <text>This finding, combined with the seasonal effect of vertical mixing on plankton succession and food-web structure, suggests that climate-controlled mixing controls DMS production over vast regions of the ocean.
</text>
